{
  "texts": [
    "DL models can be used to develop personalized treatment plans based on patient data.This can help improve treatment outcomes and reduce healthcare costs by avoiding unnecessary treatments.",
    "DL models can be used to develop automated triage systems that can identify patients who require urgent care.",
    "This can help reduce wait times for patients who require immediate attention.",
    "Telemedicine services can be integrated with electronic health records to provide a comprehensive view of patient health and treatment outcomes.",
    "This can help healthcare providers make informed decisions about patient care."
  ]
}